						               													<description>&amp;#10;            Noir Nights is a Kickstarter Project coming very soon***&amp;#10;        &amp;#10;    &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Noir Nights:Blood on the Badge is a fast paced deck building game designed by Joseph Bridges and John Gannon with artwork by John Gannon Commisions and Concepts. Noir Nights is a deck building game where players use Leads and Arrest Evidence points on cards in their deck to arrest Mobsters. It offers a dynamic play experience where players have to react and adjust their strategy accordingly.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game play is similar to other deck building games, with the player adding cards to their deck by &amp;quot;purchasing&amp;quot; them from a central deck, which has the top three cards revealed and available for purchase. When cards are removed, they are replaced with a new one from the top of the deck. Badge Honor points are earned in two ways: 1)Some Assets/Policemen cards acquired during game play are worth one or more Badge Honor points; 2) Badge Honor points can be gained by arresting Mobsters with Arrest Evidence Points featured on several of the Asset/Policeman cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
